1. System Architecture

The system follows a 3-tier architecture:

Frontend (UI Layer)
        │
        ▼
Backend (Business Logic Layer)
        │
        ▼
Database (Data Layer)
Components:
Frontend: User Interface for HR, Admin, Employees
Backend: Handles business logic, workflows, validations
Database: Stores employee, onboarding, and offboarding data
