5. System Workflow
Onboarding Flow
Employee Creation
   ↓
Document Upload
   ↓
HR Verification
   ↓
IT Setup (Email, System Access)
   ↓
Manager Assignment
   ↓
Training Completion
   ↓
Employee Activated
Offboarding Flow
Resignation Request
   ↓
Manager Approval
   ↓
HR Approval
   ↓
IT Access Revocation
   ↓
Asset Return Check
   ↓
Final Settlement
   ↓
Employee Deactivated
